        <p>Great post by Laura &#8220;@Pistachio&#8221; Fitton.  Exactly sums up why Twitter is so lovely: &#8220;For a contrived, weird and techy way to communicate, Twitter’s “passive conversation” fosters very natural, gradual relationship-building.&#8221;</p>

