<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/aug/20/">&#x27a0;</a> August 20, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="social-hardware" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://schulzeandwebb.com/blog/2007/08/20/bbc-olinda-digital-radio-social-hardware/">BBC Olinda digital radio: Social hardware</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Schulze &amp; Webb are working on an open, social digital-radio-plus-wifi prototype for the BBC.  Fascinating the way they hope to apply &#8220;open source&#8221; to hardware design.</p>

