    <div class="well" id="jaiku" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://rodbegbie.jaiku.com/">Jaiku | Rod Begbie</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>I&#8217;m taking a look at Jaiku &#8212; a Twitter-a-like status-sharer, but with deep integration into Series 60 cellphones.  It can tell people when I&#8217;m on my cellphone, warn them that I&#8217;ve put it on silent mode, or tell them my location based upon the cell tower I&#8217;m connected to.</p>

