        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.webkinz.com/index.html">Welcome to Webkinz</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>The big craze with some friends&#8217; kids &#8212; A kind-of cross between Beanie Babies, The Sims and Second Life.  Buy a cheap cuddly toy, register with the site, and bring it to life in a virtual world where you can play with it, buy it treats with pretend-money you have to &#8220;earn&#8221; and interact with your friends.  Think I&#8217;ll buy one for Joy.</p>

